HEADWORD: Thitherward
<hw>Thith"er*ward</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>To ward that
place; in that direction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They shall ask the way to Zion, with their faces
